## Mandatory Requirements

### 1. Standard Shell Layout (No Exceptions)

The Brand Shop Builder MUST use the standard page shell:


<div className={styles.root}>
  <MastHead currentSolution="Brand Shop Builder" />
  <div className={styles.appRow}>
    <AppSidebar menuItems={...} activeMenuItem={...} onMenuItemClick={...} />
    <main className={styles.main}>
      {/* page content */}
    </main>
  </div>
</div>
```

Never render the builder as a standalone full-viewport page without MastHead and AppSidebar.

### 2. Button Sizes

- Footer action buttons (Create Shelf, Save as draft, Publish): `size="medium"` (default)
- Dialog buttons (Cancel, Save as draft): `size="medium"` (default)
- Preview inline buttons (Shop now, + Add): `size="small"` (compact preview context)
- Buttons adjacent to `size="small"` form controls: `size="small"` to match

### 3. Component Compliance

All components MUST use LD 3.5 design system components:

- Buttons: `<Button>` from `@/components/ui/Button`
- Links: `<Link>` from `@/components/ui/Link`
- Link buttons: `<LinkButton>` from `@/components/ui/LinkButton`
- Icon buttons: `<IconButton>` from `@/components/ui/IconButton`
- Icons: From `@/components/icons` (Drag, ExternalLink, X, etc.)
- Form controls: `<TextField>`, `<TextArea>`, `<Select>`, `<Checkbox>` — all `size="small"`
- Dividers: `<Divider>` from `@/components/ui/Divider`

### 4. No Raw HTML Elements

Never use:
- Raw `<button>` — use `<Button>` or `<IconButton>`
- Raw `<a>` — use `<Link>` or `<LinkButton>`
- Inline SVG icons — use icons from `@/components/icons`
- Raw `<input>` / `<select>` / `<textarea>` — use LD form components

### 5. Design Tokens Only

All styling must use semantic design tokens:
- Colors: `var(--ld-semantic-color-*)`
- Spacing: `var(--ld-primitive-scale-space-*)`
- Typography: `var(--ld-semantic-font-*)`
- Border radius: `var(--ld-primitive-scale-borderradius-*)`

