## Extending the Builder

When adding new module types:

1. Add the type to `ShopModule['type']` union in `types.ts`
2. Create a config interface in `types.ts`
3. Add a preview component in `ShopPreview.tsx`
4. Add editor support in `ModuleEditor.tsx`
5. Add to the "Add section" dropdown in `ModuleList.tsx`
6. Add mock data in `mockData.ts`